937
00:38:28,308 --> 00:38:29,148
You two, be good.

938
00:38:29,228 --> 00:38:30,228
I'm leaving.

939
00:38:30,308 --> 00:38:31,107
- Bye.
- Okay.

940
00:38:31,187 --> 00:38:32,028
Bye, Mom.

941
