953
00:39:14,627 --> 00:39:15,947
You have the nerve to say that.

954
00:39:16,027 --> 00:39:17,027
Your sofa is so hard.

955
00:39:17,107 --> 00:39:18,107
I couldn't sleep on it.

956
00:39:19,627 --> 00:39:21,388
Hu Xiaojiao didn't come back all night?

957
00:39:22,027 --> 00:39:23,147
That's right.

958
00:39:23,828 --> 00:39:24,987
Does she often do that?

959
00:39:32,467 --> 00:39:33,467
Hello, honey.

960
00:39:34,428 --> 00:39:35,067
Where are you?

961
00:39:35,147 --> 00:39:35,908
Why didn't you

962
00:39:36,147 --> 00:39:37,667
come back all night?

963
00:39:37,748 --> 00:39:38,748
She's with me.

964
00:39:38,908 --> 00:39:39,908
What's up?

965
00:39:41,428 --> 00:39:42,428
U-Uncle?

966
00:39:42,748 --> 00:39:44,627
Is Xiaojiao at your place?

967
00:39:45,027 --> 00:39:45,987
Then I'm relieved.

968
00:39:46,067 --> 00:39:47,427
Anyway, she's at home, right?

969
00:39:47,507 --> 00:39:49,388
She can stay as long as she wants.

970
00:39:49,908 --> 00:39:51,147
Come over tonight.

971
00:39:51,228 --> 00:39:52,388
I have something to tell you.

972
00:39:52,987 --> 00:39:53,629
Okay, Uncle.

973
00:39:53,709 --> 00:39:55,067
I'll come over tonight.

974
00:39:55,147 --> 00:39:56,147
See you tonight.

975
00:39:56,987 --> 00:39:57,987
Qian Hao,

976
00:39:58,788 --> 00:39:59,669
I can see why you

977
00:39:59,749 --> 00:40:01,067
complained to me last night.

978
00:40:02,788 --> 00:40:03,788
Alright.

979
00:40:04,388 --> 00:40:04,908
This is

980
00:40:04,988 --> 00:40:06,067
