981
00:40:06,147 --> 00:40:07,147
It won't happen again.

982
00:40:07,868 --> 00:40:08,948
I won't drink with you.

983
00:40:09,348 --> 00:40:11,027
Be careful not to get hit by a car.

984
00:40:11,187 --> 00:40:12,187
Don't talk nonsense.

985
00:40:23,708 --> 00:40:24,708
Hello, Mom.

986
00:40:25,187 --> 00:40:26,187
Son,

987
00:40:26,268 --> 00:40:28,067
I want to discuss something with you.

988
00:40:28,748 --> 00:40:30,228
It's the thing I mentioned

989
00:40:30,308 --> 00:40:32,428
about Hu Xiaojiao being bad luck to you.

990
00:40:34,268 --> 00:40:35,228
What's the matter?

991
00:40:35,308 --> 00:40:36,308
Listen.

992
00:40:36,388 --> 00:40:38,268
I have this chat group for patients.

993
00:40:38,428 --> 00:40:40,428
There was a person
who got stomach cancer.

994
00:40:41,187 --> 00:40:43,027
Even the doctors all said
he couldn't be cured.

995
00:40:43,147 --> 00:40:44,228
But he

996
00:40:44,388 --> 00:40:45,387
found a master

997
00:40:45,467 --> 00:40:46,667
to have a fortune told.

998
00:40:47,027 --> 00:40:49,228
And as a result, he was cured.

999
00:40:49,788 --> 00:40:50,548
What's that?

1000
00:40:50,628 --> 00:40:51,828
What master?

1001
00:40:52,147 --> 00:40:53,147
Son,

1002
00:40:53,547 --> 00:40:55,627
I know about my illness.

1003
00:40:56,187 --> 00:40:57,348
Seeing doctors

1004
00:40:57,428 --> 00:40:59,067
