1005
00:41:00,027 --> 00:41:02,067
But I still want to find some hope.

1006
00:41:02,547 --> 00:41:04,428
Don't say that I'm superstitious.

1007
00:41:04,627 --> 00:41:05,668
That man in my group

1008
00:41:05,748 --> 00:41:07,228
was indeed cured.

1009
00:41:07,908 --> 00:41:09,228
I heard that the master

1010
00:41:09,308 --> 00:41:11,067
