1013
00:41:17,708 --> 00:41:18,708
When?

1014
00:41:19,308 --> 00:41:20,308
I heard that the master

1015
00:41:20,388 --> 00:41:21,868
is practicing nearby.

1016
00:41:22,147 --> 00:41:23,308
Let's go right away.

1017
00:41:23,388 --> 00:41:24,388
Okay?

1018
00:41:27,388 --> 00:41:28,268
Alright.

1019
00:41:28,348 --> 00:41:29,189
Let me tidy up.

1020
00:41:29,269 --> 00:41:30,587
I'll head out right away.

1021
