1026
00:41:48,349 --> 00:41:49,907
Look, she's skimmed off all the oil.

1027
00:41:49,987 --> 00:41:51,547
You must drink it.

1028
00:41:57,587 --> 00:41:58,947
That's more like it.

1029
00:41:59,027 --> 00:42:00,308
You have to eat something.

1030
00:42:00,467 --> 00:42:01,229
Otherwise, the baby

1031
00:42:01,309 --> 00:42:02,587
