1056
00:42:50,987 --> 00:42:52,067
If you

1057
00:42:52,147 --> 00:42:52,947
get an abortion

1058
00:42:53,027 --> 00:42:53,947
and hurt your body,

1059
00:42:54,027 --> 00:42:54,907
